{
  "stem": "1415.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "So this might have been at the very end of '39 or the beginning of '40.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And we had a hard time coming back from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "We had to take a-- a horse and buggy to come home because they wouldn't let us on a train anymore because we were Jews.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And that's the reason I told this story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "My arm never did heal well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I still have a crooked arm, but it's good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then next thing I remember is-- well, they let us stay in our house for approximately, I would say, for a year after the war started.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "They let us stay in our home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "My grandfather built his building in a beautiful section of town, which the Germans had an eye on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And as soon as the proper time came, which I would say about a year later, they evacuated us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And by that time already, an open ghetto was formed in our town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "By an open ghetto, what I mean is-- is-- is there were posters posted at certain places in our town, where Jews were not allowed to cross anymore.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] While I was still in my house, I remember little things with my cousins.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "I remember my-- little things that I passed on to my kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "I remember my cousin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "I always thought she was very mean to me, because she was a little older, and she got a chance to go to school.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And she used to come home, and-- and they had a garden.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And they put a little short picket fence around it, and I wanted to go in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And she says, you can't smell my flowers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "You're going to smell them all out.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
